{"tid":1569452,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一名警員昨晚屯門執勤期間遺失一發子彈","createTime":"2019-09-14T15:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T06:11:05.000Z","uid":68738,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bd4100245dc9dd2a95ea10d8b09bfc5ce05901c6","tid":1569452,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:31:11.000Z","msg":"2019-09-14 HKT 23:03<br />\n警方表示，一名隸屬屯門分區特遣隊警員，昨晚在屯門杯渡路及震寰路一帶執勤期間，意外遺失一發點三八口徑子彈。警方接獲報告後，立即展開調查及到現場搜尋，暫時未有發現，案件列作「遺失政府財物」，由屯門警區刑事調查隊第八隊跟進調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲市民如拾獲有關物品，應立即致電九九九或交到就近警署，又重申警隊就裝備的保管及使用有嚴格規定，會繼續跟進事作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480590-20190914.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480590-20190914.htm&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=8c2886c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480590-20190914.htm&h=a7d9397c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480590-20190914.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6baca73b60e182a8c21846e9980a0300c90e282d","tid":1569452,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:31:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa3cca1c7258be45042e5fef64579ca497551c33","tid":1569452,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:32:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/lovepopolovehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flovepopolovehk&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=4d94b9f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/lovepopolovehk</a>